{"word":"H5068 - נָדַב - nâdab - naw-dab' - Offer freely","slug":"H5068","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">נָדַב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>nâdab"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>naw-dab'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Offer freely"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E0;&#x05D3;&#x05D1; - na&#x0302;dab</b> - <i>naw-dab'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>impel</i>; hence to <i>volunteer</i> (as a soldier), to <i>present</i> spontaneously: - offer freely, be (give, make, offer self) willing (-ly)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5070\">H5070</a>, <a href=\"#/H5071\">H5071</a>, <a href=\"#/H5072\">H5072</a>, <a href=\"#/H5081\">H5081</a>, <a href=\"#/H5082\">H5082</a>, <a href=\"#/H5114\">H5114</a>"}]}